---
title: CivicRecords AI — Ingestion Pipeline Sequence (v1.1+)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Beat as Celery Beat
    participant Task as Celery Worker
    participant SR as Sync Runner
    participant Conn as Connector<br/>(REST/ODBC/FS)
    participant Pipe as Ingestion Pipeline
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Ollama as Ollama<br/>(Local LLM)

    Beat->>Task: trigger_sync(source_id) [per cron schedule]
    Task->>SR: run_sync(source_id)

    SR->>PG: load DataSource config
    SR->>Conn: authenticate()
    Conn-->>SR: auth OK

    SR->>PG: load retrying SyncFailures (cap N=100, T=90s)
    loop For each retrying failure
        SR->>Conn: fetch(source_path)
        Conn-->>SR: FetchedDocument
        SR->>Pipe: ingest_record(doc)
        Pipe->>PG: upsert Document (SELECT FOR UPDATE)
        Pipe->>Ollama: embed(chunks)
        Ollama-->>Pipe: embeddings
        Pipe->>PG: upsert Chunks + pgvector
        Pipe-->>SR: success / failure
    end

    SR->>Conn: discover(since=last_cursor)
    Conn-->>SR: [DiscoveredRecord, ...]

    loop For each discovered record
        SR->>Conn: fetch(source_path)
        Conn-->>SR: FetchedDocument
        SR->>Pipe: ingest_record(doc)
        alt New document
            Pipe->>PG: INSERT Document
            Pipe->>Ollama: embed(chunks)
            Ollama-->>Pipe: embeddings
            Pipe->>PG: INSERT Chunks + pgvector
        else Content changed
            Pipe->>PG: DELETE old Chunks (atomic)
            Pipe->>PG: UPDATE Document
            Pipe->>Ollama: embed(new chunks)
            Pipe->>PG: INSERT new Chunks + pgvector
        else No change (hash match)
            Pipe-->>SR: skip (idempotent)
        end
        alt Failure (IOError / timeout)
            SR->>PG: upsert SyncFailure(status=retrying)
        else Failure (IntegrityError)
            SR->>PG: upsert SyncFailure(status=permanently_failed)
        end
    end

    SR->>PG: advance last_sync_cursor
    SR->>PG: INSERT SyncRunLog (counts, duration)

    alt 5 consecutive full-run failures
        SR->>PG: SET sync_paused=true, sync_paused_reason
        SR->>Task: trigger circuit_open notification
    else Any success
        SR->>PG: SET consecutive_failure_count=0
    end
